      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 81,
      "enhanced_tags": [],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:07.693942"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "Oh, you mean a bad boss, someone you just can't get on with no matter how hard you try. Yes, I've had one or two over the years. Not you of course, Neil.Oh, glad to hear it, Georgina. Often this happens because workers feel they aren't listened to by managers, or it might be because most companies are hierarchies – systems of organising people according to their level of importance.Managers on top, workers down below.",
      "chunk_id": "2490c742-6fe7-4e63-8ff5-b2edacfa7ea4",
      "chunk_index": 1,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d11766ba",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_No more bosses.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 421,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "RTA",
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:07.697008"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "We'll meet a self-managing company which isn't hierarchical and has no boss, and of course we'll be learning some new vocabulary along the way.",
      "chunk_id": "35163371-9dca-4f41-9d62-bc1d15f474a5",
      "chunk_index": 2,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d11766ba",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_No more bosses.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 143,
      "enhanced_tags": [],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:07.699921"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "OK, Georgina, we'll find out later if you're right.Now, one of the first companies to experiment successfully with self-management was Californian tomato grower Morningstar.",
      "chunk_id": "2b8575ab-f937-4167-820e-11ff26a355c3",
      "chunk_index": 3,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d11766ba",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_No more bosses.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 173,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "XP",
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:07.702456"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "Because Morningstar has no bosses,",
      "chunk_id": "12e66ded-3564-4e20-b070-145748c3bdff",
      "chunk_index": 4,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d11766ba",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_No more bosses.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 34,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:07.704735"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "everything is based on requesting someone to act and then responding.This motivates and empowers workers, but also means they must keep their commitments – promises or firm decisions to do something when requested.",
      "chunk_id": "875de27c-561f-4861-b2e6-24b7f8f1b2da",
      "chunk_index": 5,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d11766ba",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_No more bosses.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 214,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "CI",
        "軟實力",
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:07.707339"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "But Dina questions whether this is true for everybody working at Morningstar.",
      "chunk_id": "c454fc67-902b-4252-8bda-a27c99f1f4ad",
      "chunk_index": 6,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d11766ba",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_No more bosses.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 77,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:07.709748"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "Having no bosses sounds great, but the extra responsibility can create more work and stress.",
      "chunk_id": "36235095-2a0b-49c4-9953-757776b7620b",
      "chunk_index": 7,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d11766ba",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_No more bosses.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 92,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "BI",
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:07.712127"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "However, other workers enjoy managing themselves and take full advantage of the system – make good use of the opportunity to improve and achieve their goals.So although having no boss sounds good, if things go wrong, there's no one to blame but yourself.",
      "chunk_id": "2336100e-24e0-4901-bfa7-faf42197ddf5",
      "chunk_index": 8,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d11766ba",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_No more bosses.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 254,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "ES"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:07.714820"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "Maybe we do need those managers after all, which reminds me of our quiz question.You asked me to estimate how much the U.S. economy loses in excess bureaucracy and managerial costs every year.And you said…C. Three trillion dollars.Which was absolutely right. Well done.And the cost keeps rising, because of course the more managers there are, the more managers you need to manage the managers.Today we've been looking at the world of self-management.",
      "chunk_id": "c2d0e767-bcb6-4b02-a178-642b0feafe02",
      "chunk_index": 9,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d11766ba",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_No more bosses.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 450,
      "enhanced_tags": [
        "UI",
        "EPS",
        "ES",
        "AI"
      ],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:07.717768"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "The world of self-management, the world of self-management.",
      "chunk_id": "dfbe712c-2102-42a7-a67f-793e227c9f44",
      "chunk_index": 10,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d11766ba",
      "original_filename": "RSS_262026947_podcast_1304_No more bosses.json",
      "collection_name": "RSS_262026947",
      "chunk_length": 59,
      "enhanced_tags": [],
      "tagged_at": "2025-07-10T14:45:07.720111"
    },
    {
      "chunk_text": "But whatever their job role or feelings about self-management, all workers are held accountable – asked to accept responsibility for their performance at work.",
      "chunk_id": "fe2ce64d-e88b-482f-838b-13c4e38a4dba",
      "chunk_index": 11,
      "episode_id": "6865015b66c1a4e8d11766ba",
